title: Chelsea Clinton Claims She Won’t Seek US Senate Seat
text:
Piers Morgan: The Media Is ‘Absolutely Determined’ To Bring Down Trump 
Reports that Chelsea Clinton would be the next member of the Clinton family to seek office swirled about in the wake of her mother’s defeat at the hands of President Donald Trump. The focus of most rumors was a possible seat in the House of Representatives. . @ChelseaClinton says she is not running for Senate. pic.twitter.com/66Y4YemN1y 
— Fox News (@FoxNews) February 11, 2017

In its gossip page speculation about a Clinton Senate bid, the Daily News quoted what it said was a source close to both families saying Clinton was “engaging in the political arena.” 
“What you’re witnessing is the beginning of Chelsea Clinton’s political career ,” the Daily News quoted its source as saying.
